{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "FirePerimeterSpread",
        "description": "Fire perimeter spread rate and fireline intensity — calculates spread rate normal to the elliptical fire perimeter and Byram's fireline intensity. Migrated from WildlandFire.jl@126976f2508ceacca6c486b21ae6da5b168c6f46:src/fire_spread_direction.jl:264 (`FirePerimeterSpread` @component). Algebraic-only: R_H, f, g, h, γ, H_A are inputs (parameters); cos_θ, sin_θ, θ, R_ψ, ψ, I_B are algebraic outputs.",
        "tags": [
            "wildland_fire",
            "spread_direction",
            "fire_perimeter",
            "algebraic"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-07T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "WildlandFire.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (polecat-ea-2l4a4)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Andrews, Patricia L. 2018. The Rothermel surface fire spread model and associated developments: A comprehensive explanation. Gen. Tech. Rep. RMRS-GTR-371. Fort Collins, CO: U.S. Department of Agriculture, Forest Service, Rocky Mountain Research Station. Table 26, pages 89-91."
            },
            {
                "citation": "Catchpole, E. A.; deMestre, N. J.; Gill, A. M. 1982. Intensity of fire at its perimeter. Australian Forest Research. 12: 47-54."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "FirePerimeterSpread": {
            "reference": {
                "citation": "Catchpole, E. A.; deMestre, N. J.; Gill, A. M. 1982. Intensity of fire at its perimeter. Australian Forest Research. 12: 47-54. (Equation forms for cos_θ, sin_θ, θ, R_ψ, ψ, I_B.) Andrews, Patricia L. 2018. The Rothermel surface fire spread model and associated developments: A comprehensive explanation. Gen. Tech. Rep. RMRS-GTR-371. Table 26, pp. 89-91.",
                "notes": "source_ref: WildlandFire.jl@126976f2508ceacca6c486b21ae6da5b168c6f46:src/fire_spread_direction.jl:264\nUpstream `FirePerimeterSpread` is an MTK `@component` whose six inputs (R_H, f, g, h, γ, H_A) are `@parameters` and whose six outputs (cos_θ, sin_θ, θ, R_ψ, ψ, I_B) are time-indexed `@variables` defined by six algebraic equations (the standalone component is observed-only with no D(x) terms). Identical equation structure preserved here; unicode identifiers (γ, θ, ψ) are preserved from the upstream `@component` declaration.\n\nThe equations follow Catchpole et al. (1982) and Andrews (2018) Table 26 pages 89-91:\n  cos_θ = (h·cos(γ)·√(h²·cos²γ + (f²−g²)·sin²γ) − f·g·sin²γ) / (h²·cos²γ + f²·sin²γ)\n  sin_θ = √(1 − cos²θ)\n  θ    = acos(cos_θ)\n  R_ψ  = R_H·h·(g·cos_θ + f) / (f·√(h²·cos²θ + f²·sin²θ))\n  ψ    = atan(f·sin_θ / (h·cos_θ))\n  I_B  = H_A·R_ψ\n\nUpstream `@constants` `one` (= 1.0) is an MTK unit-balancing literal preserved here as a zero-default parameter with its upstream value, matching the pattern used in components/wildland_fire/terrain_slope.esm where `zero_1` is similarly preserved.\n\nTolerance rationale (model-level rel=1e-12): observed-only algebraic system (no ODE integration); the equations are chains of arithmetic ops and elementary functions (cos, sin, sqrt, acos, atan) on hardware-supported intrinsics — float64 roundoff is at the ULP level (~1e-15). 1e-12 is comfortably above that and below any plausible physical-discrimination scale on m/s spread rates, radian angles, and W/m fireline intensities (typical Byram intensities range 10²–10⁵ kW/m)."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1.0e-12
            },
            "variables": {
                "R_H": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Rate of spread in direction of maximum spread (head fire)"
                },
                "f": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Ellipse semi-major axis"
                },
                "g": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Distance from focus to center"
                },
                "h": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Ellipse semi-minor axis"
                },
                "γ": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "rad",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Direction from ignition point relative to max spread direction"
                },
                "H_A": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/m^2",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Heat per unit area"
                },
                "one": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Dimensionless one (MTK unit-balancing literal preserved from upstream)"
                },
                "cos_θ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Cosine of intermediate angle θ (dimensionless)"
                },
                "sin_θ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Sine of intermediate angle θ (dimensionless)"
                },
                "θ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "rad",
                    "description": "Intermediate angle from center of ellipse"
                },
                "R_ψ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m/s",
                    "description": "Rate of spread normal to fire perimeter"
                },
                "ψ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "rad",
                    "description": "Direction normal to perimeter relative to max spread"
                },
                "I_B": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "W/m",
                    "description": "Fireline intensity (Byram)"
                }
            },
            "equations": [
                {
                    "lhs": "cos_θ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "+",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            -1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "sin",
                                                        "args": ["γ"]
                                                    },
                                                    2
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            "g",
                                            "f"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            "h",
                                            {
                                                "op": "cos",
                                                "args": ["γ"]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "sqrt",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "+",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "^",
                                                                        "args": ["h", 2]
                                                                    },
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "^",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "cos",
                                                                                "args": ["γ"]
                                                                            },
                                                                            2
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "^",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "sin",
                                                                                "args": ["γ"]
                                                                            },
                                                                            2
                                                                        ]
                                                                    },
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "+",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                                "args": ["f", 2]
                                                                            },
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                                "args": [
                                                                                    -1,
                                                                                    {
                                                                                        "op": "^",
                                                                                        "args": ["g", 2]
                                                                                    }
                                                                                ]
                                                                            }
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "+",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": ["h", 2]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "cos",
                                                        "args": ["γ"]
                                                    },
                                                    2
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "sin",
                                                        "args": ["γ"]
                                                    },
                                                    2
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": ["f", 2]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "sin_θ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "sqrt",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "+",
                                "args": [
                                    "one",
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            -1,
                                            {
                                                "op": "^",
                                                "args": ["cos_θ", 2]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "θ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "acos",
                        "args": ["cos_θ"]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "R_ψ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "h",
                                    {
                                        "op": "+",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": ["cos_θ", "g"]
                                            },
                                            "f"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "R_H"
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "sqrt",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "+",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "*",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": ["h", 2]
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": ["cos_θ", 2]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "*",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": ["sin_θ", 2]
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                "args": ["f", 2]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "f"
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "ψ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "atan",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "/",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": ["sin_θ", "f"]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": ["h", "cos_θ"]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "I_B",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": ["R_ψ", "H_A"]
                    }
                }
            ],
            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "head_fire_direction",
                    "description": "γ = 0 (head fire direction): cos_θ = 1, sin_θ = 0, θ = 0, R_ψ = R_H·h·(g+f)/(f·h) = R_H·(g+f)/f = 1.0·(50+100)/100 = 1.5 m/s, ψ = 0, I_B = H_A·R_ψ = 1.5e7 W/m.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "R_H": 1.0,
                        "f": 100.0,
                        "g": 50.0,
                        "h": 40.0,
                        "γ": 0.0,
                        "H_A": 10000000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
                    },
                    "assertions": [
                        {
                            "variable": "cos_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 1.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "sin_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R_ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 1.5
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "I_B",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 15000000.0
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "backing_fire_direction",
                    "description": "γ = π (backing fire direction): cos_θ = -1, sin_θ = 0, θ = π, R_ψ = R_H·h·(g·(-1)+f)/(f·h) = R_H·(f−g)/f = 1.0·(100−50)/100 = 0.5 m/s, ψ = 0, I_B = 5.0e6 W/m.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "R_H": 1.0,
                        "f": 100.0,
                        "g": 50.0,
                        "h": 40.0,
                        "γ": 3.141592653589793,
                        "H_A": 10000000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
                    },
                    "assertions": [
                        {
                            "variable": "cos_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": -1.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "sin_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 3.141592653589793,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R_ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.5
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.0,
                            "tolerance": {
                                "abs": 1.0e-15
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "I_B",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 5000000.0
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "flanking_direction",
                    "description": "γ = π/2 (flanking direction perpendicular to head fire): cos_θ = -g/f = -50/100 = -0.5, sin_θ = √(1−0.25) = √0.75 ≈ 0.8660254038, θ = acos(−0.5) = 2π/3 ≈ 2.0943951024, R_ψ = R_H·h·(g·cos_θ+f)/(f·√(h²·cos²θ+f²·sin²θ)) = 3/√79 ≈ 0.3375263703 m/s, ψ = atan(f·sin_θ/(h·cos_θ)) = atan(-5√3/2) ≈ −1.3438352478 rad, I_B = H_A·R_ψ ≈ 3.375263703e6 W/m.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "R_H": 1.0,
                        "f": 100.0,
                        "g": 50.0,
                        "h": 40.0,
                        "γ": 1.5707963267948966,
                        "H_A": 10000000.0
                    },
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
                    },
                    "assertions": [
                        {
                            "variable": "cos_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": -0.5
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "sin_θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.8660254037844386
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "θ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 2.0943951023931953
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R_ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 0.3375263702778072
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "ψ",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": -1.3438352477532258
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "I_B",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 3375263.7027780716
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "examples": [
                {
                    "id": "perimeter_R_psi_sweep_gamma",
                    "description": "Rate of spread normal to perimeter R_ψ (m/s) as a function of direction γ from head-fire direction (0 to π rad), at fixed ellipse geometry (f=100 m, g=50 m, h=40 m). Surfaces the cos_θ and sin_θ intermediate equations driving the R_ψ and I_B outputs across the full perimeter.",
                    "initial_state": {
                        "type": "per_variable",
                        "values": {}
                    },
                    "parameters": {},
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
                    },
                    "parameter_sweep": {
                        "type": "cartesian",
                        "dimensions": [
