                            "description": "R_ψ (m/s) vs. γ (rad) — spread rate decreases from head-fire value (R_ψ = 1.5 m/s at γ=0) through the flanking minimum (R_ψ ≈ 0.338 m/s at γ=π/2) to the backing-fire value (R_ψ = 0.5 m/s at γ=π).",
                            "x": {
                                "variable": "γ",
                                "label": "γ (rad)"
                            },
                            "y": {
                                "variable": "R_ψ",
                                "label": "R_ψ (m/s)"
                            }
                        },
                        {
